<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 09:16:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>对冲基金在不受欢迎的中国房地产部门的周转</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hedge-funds-bet-turnaround-unloved-china-property-sector-2025-02-27/</link><description>一些大型的对冲基金和投资者以低价累积了长期避免的中国物业股票，预计该行业从长时间的危机中恢复过来时，有利可图的回报。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 08:42:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hedge-funds-bet-turnaround-unloved-china-property-sector-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚在与中国的竞争中讨论安全性，与瓦努阿图的援助</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-discusses-security-aid-with-vanuatu-amid-competition-with-china-2025-02-27/</link><description>澳大利亚保证在与瓦努阿图的安全和经济会谈中，周四保证成为南太平洋最大的援助捐助者，因为堪培拉审查了美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的外国援助削减的潜在太平洋影响。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 08:20:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-discusses-security-aid-with-vanuatu-amid-competition-with-china-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国说，塔斯曼海上海军射击演习与国际法“排队”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-tasman-sea-navy-firing-drills-in-line-with-international-law-2025-02-27/</link><description>国防部的发言人周四表示，中国海军最近在澳大利亚和新西兰之间的塔斯曼海海军进行了直播演习“完全与国际法一致”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 08:15:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-tasman-sea-navy-firing-drills-in-line-with-international-law-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普对中国钢铁的新关税搅动贸易摩擦浪潮</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/trumps-new-tariffs-stir-wave-trade-frictions-against-chinese-steel-2025-02-27/</link><description>中国的巨型钢铁行业今年面临着出口的越来越大。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 08:05:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/trumps-new-tariffs-stir-wave-trade-frictions-against-chinese-steel-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普的钢铁关税危害中国的钢铁转运贸易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/trumps-steel-tariffs-imperil-chinas-steel-transshipment-trade-2025-02-27/</link><description>新的美国钢铁关税将破坏数十亿美元的供应链通过第三国将钢从中国移至美国，从而累积了全球市场的竞争，并削弱了中国挣扎的钢铁行业的重要销售来源。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 08:02:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/trumps-steel-tariffs-imperil-chinas-steel-transshipment-trade-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国的百度，CATL共同开发“竞争性”无人驾驶汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-baidu-catl-jointly-develop-competitive-driverless-vehicles-2025-02-27/</link><description>这些公司周四表示，中国的百度和电动汽车电池巨头CATL将共同探索“竞争”无人驾驶汽车和创新商业模式的开发。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 08:01:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-baidu-catl-jointly-develop-competitive-driverless-vehicles-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国商务部在与美国的交流中说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-commerce-ministry-says-communication-with-us-counterparts-2025-02-27/</link><description>该部发言人周四在新闻发布会上说，中国商务部一直在与美国同行进行沟通，当时被问及可能与华盛顿达成贸易协定。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 08:00:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-commerce-ministry-says-communication-with-us-counterparts-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>资深香港民主党和6人因2019年暴民袭击后因骚乱而入狱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/veteran-hong-kong-democrat-6-others-jailed-rioting-after-2019-mob-attack-2025-02-27/</link><description>香港法院周四判处资深民主党人林·舒克·廷（Lam Cheuk-ting）和另外六名男子因暴动而在2019年夏季被一名白衬衫暴民袭击而被判入狱数年，因为亲民主抗议活动遭受了愤怒。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 07:50:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/veteran-hong-kong-democrat-6-others-jailed-rioting-after-2019-mob-attack-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>在广告集团被弱中国击中，美国不确定性之后，WPP的股票暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/wpps-organic-revenue-drops-1-after-weak-final-quarter-2025-02-27/</link><description>AD Group WPP报告说，在最后一个季度令人失望的最后一季度后，有机收入的下降幅度较差，当时它受到客户酌处支出较弱的袭击，并表示必须谨慎行事，大约在2025年左右，其股份却大幅下降。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 07:30:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/wpps-organic-revenue-drops-1-after-weak-final-quarter-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促我们停止关税调查铜进口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-urges-us-halt-tariff-probe-into-copper-imports-2025-02-27/</link><description>中国周四敦促美国停止对铜进口的潜在新关税进行调查，以重建美国的关键金属生产，誓言是否要报复中国实体是否陷入了税款中。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 07:29:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-urges-us-halt-tariff-probe-into-copper-imports-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>印度合同制造商在中国寻求政府支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/indias-contract-drug-makers-seek-government-support-china-fight-2025-02-27/</link><description>印度的合同制药商已敦促政府消除监管障碍，并在许多全球制药公司依靠国家以减少对中国的依赖的时候，以更快地批准重要的原料进口。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 07:09:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/indias-contract-drug-makers-seek-government-support-china-fight-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>泰国总理说，必须遵循对乌格尔人的关注</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-pm-says-human-rights-principles-must-be-followed-amid-concern-over-fate-2025-02-27/</link><description>泰国总理周四表示，必须遵循国际标准和人权原则，以回应激进主义者提出的担忧，即持有的48个Uyghurs已有十多年的时间被暗中驱逐到中国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 06:11:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-pm-says-human-rights-principles-must-be-followed-amid-concern-over-fate-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinas-baidu-launch-upgraded-ai-ernie-model-mid-march-source-says-2025-02-27/</link><description>中国的百度将在3月中旬推出其下一代人工智能模型Ernie，这将在推理等领域的能力上提高。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 06:00:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinas-baidu-launch-upgraded-ai-ernie-model-mid-march-source-says-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国“绿色”喷气燃料工厂在缺乏政策的情况下推迟初创企业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/china-green-jet-fuel-plants-push-back-start-up-amid-lack-policy-2025-02-27/</link><description>由于缺乏政府政策指导，几家可持续航空燃料（SAF）工厂的中国建造者正在推迟起步，这限制了他们在国内营销或出口燃料。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 05:20:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/china-green-jet-fuel-plants-push-back-start-up-amid-lack-policy-2025-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>《金融时报》报道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-curbs-us-stock-listings-homegrown-companies-financial-times-reports-2025-02-27/</link><description>《金融时报》周四报道，中国的证券监管机构已削减了小型本土公司在美国证券交易所上市的小型本土公司，因为其中许多人成为价格钉的车辆，造成了美国投资者的巨大损失。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 05:19:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-curbs-us-stock-listings-homegrown-companies-financial-times-reports-2025-02-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>